<HEADLINE>
<P>
VALLEY PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 CDI Temporary Services promoted Sharon Heller to vice president in charge of 
the company's Southern California operations, which are based in Westlake 
Village. She previously was district manager of CDI's Simi Valley and Westlake 
Village branch offices. 
</P>
<P>
CDI, based in Philadelphia, provides workers and other temporary business 
services. The company has 10 branches in Southern California. 
</P>
</TEXT>
