<P>
 James R. Pingel was named vice president and corporate controller of Shamrock 
Broadcasting in Burbank. 
</P>
<P>
Shamrock Broadcasting is the radio and television operation of Shamrock 
Holdings, a Burbank firm owned by the Roy E. Disney family. The company 
operates three television stations and 15 radio stations nationwide. 
