</P>
<P>
The Times incorrectly reported Tuesday that the Orange County Transit District 
intends to impose a 5-cent transfer fee for changing buses. There will be no 
such fee. In the same story, the amount of Southern California Rapid Transit 
District costs that are recovered through fare-box revenue was misstated. It is 
40%, the RTD said. 
